      "PAN AM\nThe individual whose photograph appears on\nthis identification card is an employes of Pan\nAmerican World Airways, with Company se\nniority date shown. This card is the property\nof Pan American World Airways and must be\nsurrendered upon termination of employment.\nIt is valid only when signed by the employee.\nLoss of this card must be reported immedi\nately to your personnel department or to your\nappropriate station official.\nEmployee Signature\nJuders Cok"
